node.text:
♥.
1️⃣🌼3 X 12ᴇᴀᴄʜ sɪᴅᴇ ~ Alternating reverse lunges + battle-ropes 
2️⃣🌼3 X 45sec.~ Squat Pulses (3) + Squat Jumps (2)
3️⃣🌼3 X 45sec.~ Planks
4️⃣🌼3 X 45sec.~ Side-to-side jumps
5️⃣🌼3 X 12~ Reverse Crunches
6️⃣🌼3 X 12~ Banded V-ups
♥.
Concentrating on pain that exists within your body, sends electrical currents to your mind that continues producing the pain. 🌈Likewise, focusing on the p̆̈ŏ̈s̆̈ĭ̈t̆̈ĭ̈v̆̈ĕ̈, sends  electrical signals to your mind that continues producing more happy/positive feelings and thoughts!🥰… Be conscious of the conversation you are continually having with yourself. Love, happiness, compassion and everything in between starts within; then share it with the world 🥰

node.text:
Been using this extra time at home to get back into a few practices I used to have & used to love 🙃 - ☝🏼 of which is yoga 🤍 
I used to actually teach yoga as a class at my school (technically the football coach was the teacher but I spent EVERYDAY in a dance studio for YEARS and took yoga many many times, so in exchange for being a teachers pet & and A+ I taught the class and REALLY actually LOVED IT 🙂 definitely one of the coolest experiences in HS)

I’m rusty now 🕸🤗 but diving right back into it 🥰

node.text:
.🗓🌱.
We all find ourselves in a time that is full of unchartered territory, making things like getting the proper nutrient-rich foods in our regular diet a bit more trying then usual.
.💚.
For myself, I have never been the worlds best chef by any means, and with the current changes in availability of what products I am able to find in stores, making a balanced meal has become pretty darn difficult at times.
.🍠🥦🍗.
We are beyond blessed to have so many amazing friends in our lives that have businesses built around healthy lifestyles, which has really made this whole experience so much more bearable.
.🙏🏼❤️.
One of our good friends @toddabrams is one of those incredible humans in our lives who hasn’t just been an incredible friend and an amazing person to learn from but has also been a blessing with keeping our meals on track during these times.
.🙂🙌🏼.
Todd started @iconmeals as a company of custom, nutritional and freshly prepared meals (along with a whole array of delicious and low-sugar & high-protein snacks) that you can create personally to your own dietary needs and preferences that get delivered straight to your front door in a sealed cooler, ready to eat- in just a few quick minutes.
. 🚏🚛.
In my house, we have personally been eating our share of Icon Meals for some time and absolutely LOVE THEM, but now more then ever, it has truly been a lifesaver to have them stocked in our kitchen, so that my family is able to keep our meals nutritionally balanced so that we all can stay healthy & feeling our best.
.🧑‍🍳.
The best part is that, just like me, you don’t have to be a professional chef to eat like one! And the deliveries are still making their way to your door within a few short days after ordering!
.🥰.
I just want to say Thank You to all the amazing people & businesses such as Icon Meals, who have put their hearts into doing everything they can to keep as many of us healthier and happier then ever during this times.
.🙂🙌🏼.
I hope everyone is keeping their heads up & hoping that all these suggestions & tips help make these times inside a whole lot more manageable and pleasant.

node.title: Tips to Keeping Healthy Meals Part of Your Daily Routine

node.text:
With all of us stuck in our homes the past few days/ the entire week/or more, many of us are finding that making the best nutritional choices as our food options begin to dwindle, is really starting to become quiet the task 🌈🥥.
When our friend @fensterjeff told us that him and the 😋 @everbowlcraftsuperfood family really wanted to do what they could to not let this quarantine take the sweetness out of the tasty treats that many of us enjoy regularly at all the wonderful Everbowl locations; I couldn’t have been more onboard with the idea of them making packets of their wonderful açaí & fruit mixes available to the public, that had all the fixings for easy to create Superfood bowls that we all can get shipped directly to our front doors 🚛 and be made in the comfort of our own kitchens!🧑‍🍳
🌈🥥.
As a friend and as someone who is truly obsessed with Everbowls’, I thought there was no better way to make our quick trip to pick up some food supplies for our house one that wouldn’t just brighten up my day and fill my kitchen with these delicious snacks that we love so much, but that I could hopefully do the same by getting the word out for everyone else who would also enjoy these delightful antioxidant-packed treats 🙃🤗
🌈🥥.
Beyond being insanely delicious, I have so much respect & admiration for how much dedication, compassion and genuine care that Jeff and his entire team built Everbowl on, and of course, I am always more then happy to do what I can to bring a little extra sweetness and a whole lot of 🍓🥝💥antioxidants & 🍍🥥Nutrients into as many kitchens as we can to keep this time inside one that is that much more enjoyable! All while helping to keep our immune systems running strong and keeping us all feeling just a little more happy and healthy!
🌈🥥.
The Açaí & Fruit Packets will be available online for purchase thru their site TOMORROW (for shipping in the San Diego area) and will be available to the rest of us in the states within the next week!
🌈🥥.Sending everyone wishes of health & happiness and hope everyone is able to get this packets of joy sent to their homes to make your days inside a whole lot sweeter 🥰

node.title: ☀️ Bringing Happiness & Healthy snacks straight to You🥰🍓🍍🥝🥥🌈🚛😋
